Package: MR.SPI
Type: Package
Title: Mendelian randomization that select valid IVs and perform post-selection inference
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Minhao Yao, Zijian Guo, Zhonghua Liu
Maintainer: Minhao Yao <mhyao@connect.hku.hk>
Description: This package provides functions for two sample Mendelian randomization with invalid instrumental variables, which can select valid IVs and provide robust confidence intervals of the causal effect.
